name:                begin
stack:               ( -- )
return stack:        ( -- )
string stack:        ( -- )
contexts:            compileonly
category:            flow control

decription:          initiate one of these flow control constructs:
                     begin ... again
                     begin ... until
                     begin ... while ... repeat

standard:            no
deviation:           Compilation: ( C: -- dest )
                     Put the next location for a transfer of control, dest,
                     onto the control flow stack.

                     yoda has no concept of branch destinations and can't
                     therefore stack them.
